    <h2>About Kharina Secondary School</h2>
 
    <p>
		Founded in 1982, Kharina Secondary School is a public secondary school located in Northdale, Pietermaritzburg, South Africa. It is a valid, registered and prosperous School under the leadership of the Principal R.Govender, with 47 members of staff and 1223 learners. 
	</p>
    <p>
		Kharina Secondary is a public school, a quintile level 5 and a Fee-Paying school.
		The main source of income for the school is through government funding, by charging 
		school fees and doing other reasonable forms of fund-raising. The school fund is a 
		combination of school fees, the fundraising money and donations. From having an Indian ethnic identity in the early years, the school has evolved into an education service provider that presently accommodates 90% African learners.
	</p>
	<p>	
		The progress of each learner is monitored and facilitated by an expert academic empowerment team and well-educated teachers.Kharina Secondary School is an ordinary secondary school specializing in comprehensive subjects. The school provides quality teaching in classrooms and professional coaching on the sport field for learners and it is also creative in offering a curriculum designed to suit learners. <br>

		Subject packages that include isiZulu, Tourism, Business Studies, Consumer Studies and 
		Computer Applications Technology are proving to be popular and directly related to the 
		service industry. The school has forged extremely supportive partnerships with business 
		houses and religious organization that have identified with the excellence of the school and 
		vast needs of its learners.
	</p>
	<p>The focus of education at Kharina Secondary is to provide students with opportunities to learn and succeed in an healthy environment regardless of ability, gender, race or special need. By setting high standards of attainment, providing a broadly based and balanced curriculum, the students are taught and given the concepts, knowledge and skills to be confident in their world.</p>
